description: Bumping out into the narrow passage along this piered tent is a a narrow table piled with some of the goods handmade by the merchant owner of this structure.  Sunlight flashes off the water, sending reflections up and into the rolled-up window openings cut into both sides of the walls.  Underfoot, the floor gives slightly as other customers walk from one end to the other.
